---

## File Structure
The following file structure is used for this model to ensure compatibility with Model Manager:

```
models/
    player/
        [class_name]/
            [model_files]
materials/
    models/
        player/
            [class_name]/
                [texture_files]
```

- **`models/` Directory:** Contains the model files (`.mdl`, `.vtx`, `.vvd`, etc.).  
- **`materials/` Directory:** Contains the corresponding texture files (`.vtf`, `.vmt`, etc.).

Ensure you place the contents of this folder in the correct directories of your server or Model Manager setup to avoid issues.

---

## Usage
1. Place the **`models/`** and **`materials/`** folders from this package into your TF2 server's custom directory or the appropriate directory for Model Manager.
2. Edit your Model Manager configuration file to reference this model. For example:
   ```json
   {
       "model_name": "[Model Name]",
       "class": "[class_name]",
       "path": "models/player/[class_name]/[model_name].mdl"
   }
   ```
3. Restart the server to apply the changes.

